lead_paragraph: The Swiss franc is likely to hold steady or ease this year, Swiss National Bank Chairman Thomas Jordan said in an interview with Swiss radio SRF on Saturday.

headline.main: SNB's Jordan Says Swiss Franc to Stagnate or Weaken This Year
